WEBVTT

1
00:04:03.369 --> 00:04:05.502 
又或者是被全世界孤立的"病态菲尔"
Or the universally ostracized Ill Phil.

2
00:04:09.007 --> 00:04:10.539 
真的是孤家寡人
Truly a nation of one.

3
00:04:12.142 --> 00:04:16.110 
但有些地方是我不能去的
And there were some places I simply couldn't go.

4
00:04:16.112 --> 00:04:18.579 
比如学校的餐厅
Like the cafeteria.

5
00:04:18.581 --> 00:04:21.381 
这里的每一寸土地都是争议领土
Every last square inch of it was disputed territory.

6
00:04:22.216 --> 00:04:24.150 
这就像克里米亚 克什米尔
It was Crimea, Kashmir,

7
00:04:24.152 --> 00:04:26.232 
还有加沙地带的混合体
and the Gaza Strip all rolled into one.

8
00:04:27.253 --> 00:04:30.655 
当然还包括有海盗出没的那片印度洋
Also the part of the Indian Ocean with pirates.

9
00:04:30.657 --> 00:04:34.558 
是"菲利普船长"电影那种海盗 不是"加勒比海盗"那种
Captain Phillips pirates, not Pirates of the Caribbean.

